{"tid":250974,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個女仔令我有兩次失戀既感覺","createTime":"2017-05-20T13:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T14:33:39.000Z","uid":64758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb140fc1151cf450c4a2d8c4adc78cab855a9109","tid":250974,"uid":64758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"我既初戀同我分左手三年到<br />\n但我一直都忘記唔到佢<br />\n最近佢同左我一個識左十幾年既兄弟一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兄弟都知我仲好愛佢 所以都不停同我道歉<br />\n話唔想無左我呢個兄弟<br />\n我又無資格嬲佢地 最後只可以懶係君子咁祝佢地<br />\n同個兄弟講 如果你對佢唔好就真心無兄弟做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但算啦 我都唔想因爲我影響佢地<br />\n一個人痛苦總好過三個人辛苦既<br />\n而家心情就好似餘下空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n    Sor 我講野1999希望巴絲們睇得明<br />\n我只係想抒發下呢一刻既感受"},{"pid":"fd228098fff6cbdd3afe0c679b34f5555f06f132","tid":250974,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span>"},{"pid":"eb11d6078a53a9b01de3f54ac40817b295fd3ca7","tid":250974,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭死</span></span>"},{"pid":"05d2d85dca95df29fc1618d3dc5bb77f308e2dc7","tid":250974,"uid":105812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:01:35.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro <br />\n就算拍過第二個都忘記唔到個初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個初戀又比識幾年既fd食左"},{"pid":"fc5e50fc76a2e211aa254a8e36a7f902b9f57bfa","tid":250974,"uid":64758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know